query:
SELECT r.id, r.province_id
                FROM regencies r
                WHERE r.province_id = $3
                  AND (r.name ILIKE $1
                       OR r.name ILIKE $2
                       OR r.name ILIKE '%' || $1 || '%')
                ORDER BY
                    CASE
                        WHEN r.name ILIKE $1 THEN 1
                        WHEN r.name ILIKE $2 THEN 2
                        ELSE 3
                    END
                LIMIT 1
